      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presented in exemplary, showroom-grade condition, this vehicle represents a rare opportunity for the discerning collector. Meticulously maintained and preserved to the highest standards, it exhibits an uncompromising level of aesthetic and mechanical refinement. Every detail, from the flawless exterior finish to the pristine interior appointments, reflects a legacy of careful stewardship. This is an investment-grade acquisition for those who demand nothing less than perfection.",
