    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\ude97 I\u2019m honestly so excited to show you this absolute stunner. It\u2019s been my pride and joy and is in truly flawless condition\u2014honestly, it still feels like it just rolled off the lot! It drives like a dream and has been pampered every single day. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that looks and feels brand new without the dealership headache, this is the one for you. Drop me a message and come take a look, you won\u2019t be disappointed! \u2728",
      "price": 46500.0,
