      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This E46 M3 represents a superlative example of the S54-powered icon. The high-revving 3.2L atmospheric inline-six features a double-VANOS system in peak mechanical synchronization, delivering linear power through a precise Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox. The chassis integrity is uncompromising, with a factory-verified rear subframe and a suspension geometry that retains its original rigidity. Finished in Carbon Black Metallic, the exterior displays no clear-coat degradation, while the Nappa leather interior remains supple with zero bolster wear. Recent proactive service includes rod bearing replacement and a comprehensive valve clearance adjustment, ensuring this machine operates at its 8,000 RPM redline with absolute composure and technical perfection.",
